name: Levi'sAssistant
0:
”Alexa, ask Levi’s can I exchange my order?”
”Alexa, ask Levi's to find me pair of jeans?”
”Alexa, ask Levi's to find the nearest store?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: levi's
des: Use Alexa to get answers to common questions about our services. Get help on return policy, how to use gift cards, available payment methods, and more. Get help on finding a pair of jeans. Get help on finding the nearest store. Get help with tracking your order. Get information on the latest promotions.
